#      WITH this guard: graceful degradation. The frontend is truly a
#      zero-risk addition. It cannot crash the server under ANY condition.
#
#   3. str(WEB_DIR) converts the Path object to a string, which is what
#      Starlette's StaticFiles expects (it accepts both str and Path,
#      but str is the safest for cross-version compatibility).
